- Everyone okay?
- What just happened?

494
00:50:52,240 --> 00:50:53,720
Waylander.

495
00:50:57,200 --> 00:50:58,840
It's all right.
We just overshot it.

496
00:50:58,880 --> 00:51:00,320
We'll turn around
and go back.

497
00:51:02,280 --> 00:51:03,840
Hang on.

498
00:51:04,920 --> 00:51:07,680
<i>[Rumbling]</i>

499
00:51:11,520 --> 00:51:13,440
Oh my God.

500
00:51:13,520 --> 00:51:15,840
Solaris is gone.

501
00:51:15,920 --> 00:51:19,040
Gone?
It can't be gone.

502
00:51:19,120 --> 00:51:21,040
Look for yourself.
It's gone.

503
00:51:21,080 --> 00:51:24,120
What are we
going to do?

504
00:51:29,680 --> 00:51:32,000
Lou, what sort of damage
we looking at?

505
00:51:33,720 --> 00:51:35,760
I'm sending out
a distress beacon.

506
00:51:35,800 --> 00:51:39,960
- Lou?
- We've lost our entire port pontoon.

507
00:51:40,040 --> 00:51:41,840
The internal pressure
is stable.

508
00:51:41,880 --> 00:51:43,640
Our main thrusters
are off-line.

509
00:51:43,720 --> 00:51:45,560
- Life support?
- We should be okay for awhile.

510
00:51:45,600 --> 00:51:48,080
- But he's out there.
- We're going to be fine.

511
00:51:48,120 --> 00:51:49,680
We're in a high volume
traffic Lane,

512
