another ship's gonna come by.
I'm sure of it!

513
00:51:55,200 --> 00:51:57,040
- We're going to be safe here.
- [Banging]

514
00:51:57,080 --> 00:51:58,680
[Hysterical screaming]

515
00:52:00,360 --> 00:52:02,000
Shut up!

516
00:52:18,800 --> 00:52:21,080
<i>- What are you doing?
- Shh.</i>

517
00:52:42,040 --> 00:52:45,400
- Maybe he gave up.
- You really think so?

518
00:52:45,480 --> 00:52:47,000
Shh, shh, shh.

519
00:52:57,840 --> 00:52:59,960
I don't think
he's out there.

520
00:53:00,040 --> 00:53:03,760
Why don't you just stick your
head out and have a peek?

521
00:53:16,200 --> 00:53:18,360
Oh my God! Go!

522
00:53:20,040 --> 00:53:22,040
<i>Waylander:
Go, come on, go!</i>

523
00:53:22,120 --> 00:53:24,520
<i>Move it, move it!
Come on!</i>

524
00:53:24,600 --> 00:53:26,200
Let's go!

525
00:53:42,920 --> 00:53:45,240
Where's Professor Lowe?

526
00:53:52,480 --> 00:53:54,240
Hi.

527
00:53:57,760 --> 00:54:00,120
Look, have you considered
how valuable you are?

528
00:54:00,160 --> 00:54:02,080
<i>Fame, money.</i>

529
00:54:02,160 --> 00:54:05,400
With my help
you could have it all.

530
00:54:06,920 --> 00:54:09,080
I know people.
I have connections.

531
00:54:09,160 --> 00:54:11,800
Together we could
make a fortune.

532
00:54:17,120 --> 00:54:18,680
Oh, shit.

533
00:54:19,720 --> 00:54:22,320
Oh, you want
your machete back?

534
00:54:22,360 --> 00:54:25,320
Shit, it's yours!
Take it!

535
00:54:25,400 --> 00:54:29,240
Just remember
who saved it for you.

536
00:54:30,400 --> 00:54:32,360
Guys, it's okay.

537
00:54:32,440 --> 00:54:34,240
He just wanted his
machete back!

538
00:54:35,160 --> 00:54:36,400
Whew.

539
00:54:36,440 --> 00:54:38,640
<i>I'm-- I'm--</i>

540
00:54:38,680 --> 00:54:40,360
I'm gonna go back
to my room.

541
