'Cause stoney's
going to meet me there.

542
00:54:42,280 --> 00:54:44,440
<i>[Lowe screams]</i>

543
00:54:47,800 --> 00:54:49,960
All right, look.
How do we get off this ship?

544
00:54:50,040 --> 00:54:52,800
- I don't know.
- Could you beam us off or something?

545
00:54:52,880 --> 00:54:54,080
"Beam us off"?

546
00:55:01,800 --> 00:55:03,800
The shuttle.

547
00:55:05,000 --> 00:55:06,200
Hell yeah.
The shuttle.

548
00:55:06,280 --> 00:55:08,280
- What about it, crutch?
- Yeah.

549
00:55:08,360 --> 00:55:10,160
I can do pre-launch
from the bridge.

550
00:55:10,200 --> 00:55:12,600
Good, good. The rest of us
will head to the shuttle.

551
00:55:12,680 --> 00:55:15,400
- We'll start the launch list.
- I'm with you, crutch.

552
00:55:16,920 --> 00:55:18,560
[Gasps]

553
