these walkways.

701
01:07:44,440 --> 01:07:47,440
- You can't just disconnect them.
- We could blow it up.

702
01:07:47,480 --> 01:07:51,040
- There's plenty of macrocharge in the weapons hold.
- This could work.

703
01:07:51,120 --> 01:07:54,240
Tiamat, we're going
to try something here.

704
01:07:54,320 --> 01:07:56,640
If you're game, maintain your
current course and speed,

705
01:07:56,720 --> 01:07:59,200
and hopefully we'll see you
when you get here.

706
01:07:59,280 --> 01:08:01,240
<i>Copy.
See you in 45 minutes.</i>

707
01:08:01,280 --> 01:08:02,960
<i>- Good luck, grendel.
- Thanks.</i>

708
01:08:03,000 --> 01:08:05,600
- Let's blow the walkways.
- Come on.

709
01:08:17,560 --> 01:08:19,960
<i>[Electrical static]</i>

710
01:09:04,600 --> 01:09:07,640
Let's put up separate charges.
Who's got the remote?

711
01:09:07,680 --> 01:09:09,960
- Right here.
