712
01:09:51,120 --> 01:09:53,800
<i>[Rumbling]</i>

713
01:10:19,520 --> 01:10:21,680
- All set.
- Good to go.

714
01:10:21,720 --> 01:10:24,200
Hold together, baby.

715
01:10:39,640 --> 01:10:42,040
Impossible.
It's dead.

716
01:10:42,080 --> 01:10:45,080
I'd say he got better.
He's been modified.

717
01:10:45,160 --> 01:10:46,560
Oh, you think?

718
01:10:49,680 --> 01:10:53,160
- Can you take him?
- I could try.

719
01:11:11,520 --> 01:11:13,120
You guys might want to run.

720
01:11:15,320 --> 01:11:16,640
Kay-Em!

721
01:11:20,080 --> 01:11:21,560
No!

722
01:11:24,600 --> 01:11:26,440
Janessa:
Waylander!

723
01:11:26,520 --> 01:11:28,600
Brodski, get in here, now!

724
01:11:28,640 --> 01:11:31,000
Come on, guys!
Come on!

725
01:11:39,960 --> 01:11:41,480
What the hell
is going on?!

726
01:11:41,560 --> 01:11:43,800
Jason fucking Voorhees,
that's what's going on!

727
01:11:45,800 --> 01:11:48,600
- Blow the charges!
- Waylander's got the trigger!

728
01:11:50,240 --> 01:11:51,840
Hey...

729
01:11:51,920 --> 01:11:53,920
Asshole.

730
01:12:14,200 --> 01:12:16,520
<i>- [Alarms blare]
- [Sighs]</i>

731
01:12:28,680 --> 01:12:30,680
I think she's holding.

732
01:12:34,520 --> 01:12:36,640
I think we're finally okay.

733
01:12:39,240 --> 01:12:41,320
I'd clap if I could.

734
01:12:44,920 --> 01:12:47,280
Tiamat to grendel.
Come in, grendel.

735
01:12:47,320 --> 01:12:49,080
We have you vectored
for approach

736
01:12:49,120 --> 01:12:50,440
and emergency docking.

737
01:12:52,280 --> 01:12:54,360
You ready to get off
that boat?

738
01:12:54,440 --> 01:12:58,040
Yeah, let's go home.

739
01:13:04,640 --> 01:13:07,440
Holy shit!
We got to go! Now!

740
01:13:07,480 --> 01:13:10,040
[Screaming]

741
01:13:22,360 --> 01:13:23,800
Janessa!

742
01:13:39,640 --> 01:13:42,560
- Janessa!
- Don't let go!

743
